Theme Name: Booty
Description: A responsive, HTML5 Ushahidi theme based on the Twitter Bootstrap framework.
Demo: http://rrbaker.com
Version: 1.0 alpha
Author: Rob Baker
Author Email: rob@rrbaker.com

Notes
---

*** STILL AN ALPHA VERSION; VERY MUCH A WORK IN PROGRESS

Strapped is developer for Ushahidi v2.4. Previous versions will not work because older versions of the platform ran on older versions of jQuery.


Installation
---
1. Download theme
2. Unpack the theme archive (.zip or .gz)
3. Upload the entire "strapped" folder the to the "themes" folder of your Ushahidi application
4. Log in to the administration of your instance and switch to the "Strapped" theme under "Addons -> Themes".
